trans-unit.source: The ForestTrustRelationshipInformation class contains information about a trust relationship between two <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ForestTrustRelationshipInformation innehåller information om en förtroenderelation mellan två <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Gets the excluded top-level names in the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar uteslutna översta namn i den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: A read/write <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection"></xref> that contains the excluded top-level names in the current object.
trans-unit.target: Läsning och skrivning <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection"> </xref> som innehåller exkluderade översta namnen i det aktuella objektet.

trans-unit.source: Commits any changes to the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation"></xref> properties to the Active Directory Domain Services store.
trans-unit.target: Sparar ändringar i <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation"> </xref> egenskaper i arkivet för Active Directory Domain Services.

trans-unit.source: A call to the underlying directory service resulted in an error.
trans-unit.target: Ett anrop till den underliggande katalogtjänsten resulterade i ett fel.

trans-unit.source: A collision occurred with an existing trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Kollision uppstod med en betrodd relation.

trans-unit.source: Gets the top-level names in the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar de översta namn i den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: A read-only <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollection"></xref> object that contains the top-level names in the current object.
trans-unit.target: En skrivskyddad <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollection"> </xref> objekt som innehåller namnen på översta nivån i det aktuella objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the trusted domain information for this <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar betrodd domän-information för den här <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: A read-only <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInfoCollection"></xref> object that contains the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation"></xref> object for the current object.
trans-unit.target: En skrivskyddad <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInfoCollection"> </xref> objekt som innehåller den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation"> </xref> objekt för det aktuella objektet.
